Package: convenience
Title: A small collection of diverse functions for more convenient working in R
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: person("Christian", "Thiele", , "contme109@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Shortcuts to the as.numeric and as.character functions, quick
    Granger-Causality testing, creation of interaction variables and easier checking
    and storing of objects in the workspace.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    vars,
    xts,
    stringr,
    lmtest,
    SOAR
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests:
    h2o,
    testthat,
    tibble
